<div class='alert-message block-message success'>
  <p><strong> You have successfully completed the purchase. </strong> </p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      Your order number is #<strong><%= @order.number %></strong>. Please note down this number and use this order
      number in case you need to contact us.
    </li>
    <li>
      Your credit card was charged
      <strong><%= number_to_currency(@order.creditcard_transactions.first.amount) %> </strong> .
    </li>
    <li>
      In the credit card statement name of the company would appear as
      <strong><%= @order.payment_method.preferred_company_name_on_creditcard_statement %></strong> .
    </li>
    <li>
      An invoice is being sent to <strong><%= @order.email %></strong> .
    </li>
  </ul>
</div>
